description: Any comments relevant to this submission
First Name of the Primary Investigator
Last Name of the Primary Investigator
Email address of the Primary Investigator
List of exRNA grants; Choose Non-ERCC Funded Study if your grant does not fall under the list of Common Fund ERCC Grants. Provide more information in the Notes.

State - type the full name or 2-letter code of a US State. This field is a look-ahead search box that connects to BioPortal and retrieves a list of correct ontology terms for all states in the USA. For non-US states, leave this field blank and enter state name in the sub-property "Other State"
Country - type the full name of the country. This field is a look-ahead search box that connects to BioPortal and retrieves a list of correct ontology terms for all countries in the world.
